targets.query:
from(bucket: "usv")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "schneider")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "InputFrequency")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["agent_host"] == "${Host_Schneider}")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value / 10.0 }))
  |> yield(name: "mean")
